-Each participant enters their name and bid amount.
-The program asks if there are more bidders. If "yes," it clears the screen for the next bidder to input.
-Once all bids are submitted, the program announces the winner and their bid.

Example:
Welcome to the secret auction program!
What is your name? : Alice
What is your bid? : $ 250
Are there any other bidders? Type 'yes' or 'no': yes

<Screen clears for the next bidder>

What is your name? : Bob
What is your bid? : $ 300
Are there any other bidders? Type 'yes' or 'no': no
The winner is Bob with a bid of $300.
